rows.label: qev030402_MSG0001
rows.name:
You took command of situation.
My father has sent mighty hero to aid me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030402_SEL0011
rows.name:
Ask Uzoma why the Ganglion
were trying to recruit him.

rows.label: qev030402_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Uzoma to hurry back to his people.

rows.label: qev030402_MSG0002
rows.name:
I am son of Tree Clan chieftain.
If I turned traitor, it would divide clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030402_MSG0003
rows.name: They are fools. We are not cowards. We will not bow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030402_MSG0004
rows.name:
Thank you again. My father will be pleased.
I must hurry home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030402_MSG0005
rows.name:
Yes. My father will be pleased to see me.
Safe travels to you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030402_MSG0006
rows.name:
You are bearer of dolphera's wisdom.
I hope we meet again soon.[ST:wait ]
